title: Lottery Director Professional 4.0
description:
ABOUT THIS GAME:

Complete game tracking for Lotto and Pick-3/4. Wins, trends,
automatic scanning. Automatic wheeling and filtering. Supports
over 240 games, ready to play. Contains more than 800 wheeling
systems. Plus, automatically generates, tests, and plays your
own custom wheels. Full help, online guidebooks, plus &#039;Tips and
Strategies&#039; and complete player support.
